data.description: The South Florida lifestyle awaits you at this updated and well-maintained two-story home on an oversized lot in Colors of Rainbow Lakes. Enjoy a serene lake view from multiple rooms. With lots of natural light, the floor plan includes large bedrooms and a flexible loft/office space that could easily be converted into a fourth bedroom. As you enter the main living space, vaulted ceilings give an airy feel and the staircase is wide and open. Next to the kitchen, you'll find a comfortable den/TV room with easy access to outdoor space along the lake. Enjoy your morning beverage in the sunroom as you gaze out onto the lake to spot spoonbills, blue herons and other wildlife. Includes whole house generator and on-demand hot water heater for unlimited hot water.
